<h1>BurGer Time</h1>

<h3>Add Burgers to the list and save them for later .</h3>
<h3>Or eat them and erase them from your thoughts due to regret.</h3>

<ul>
  {{#each burger}}
  	<li>
  	   <p>ID: {{this.id}}</p>
       <p>Task: {{this.burger_name}}</p>
  	</li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<form action="/" method="POST">
	<textarea type="text" name="task"></textarea>

	<button type="submit">Submit</button>
</form>